      <h1 class="h2">About Us</h1>
   </div>
   <div class="content">
      <p>People in the world were facing first ever lockdown of their lives in mid 2020s. At that time, Mrs. Kshipra Joshi, founder of Kotton Glitters has come up with the idea of starting her own venture by selling masks from home in her society, based in Noida (Uttar Pradesh), India where people have just started going outside to buy basic necessities. Slowly as she thought I can do something big as entrepreneur, she has started her own venture and named it KOTTON GLITTERS BY KSHIPRA.</p>
      <p>Like every other entrepreneur, she has run some trials, what would be the best material for skin, who will be my customer, from where to procure and so on. As every other person was cursing corona because of slowing their business growth rate, the lockdown helped Kshipra; her husband, Mr. Manish Sharma, was working from home and helped Kshipra in strategize things. After few days, she and her sisters, who were together with her in every thick and thin decided to go with the name “Kotton Glitters-House of Cotton by Kshipra”.</p>
      <p>Cotton is a low maintenance, powerhouse fabric. It doesn’t irritate your skin and unlike synthetic materials, lets your skin breathe easy. For women suffering from hot flashes, cotton is a great choice.</p>
      <p>Sometimes road of life takes an unexpected turn and you have no choice but to follow it to end up in the place you are supposed to be. On the midnight of 08.12.2021, Kshipra, Manish and their five years old daughter were driving back to their home from a relative’s place, a tragic accident has end up their lives but fortunately their daughter has escaped safely. In their memory, Kotton Glitters- House of Cotton by Kshipra will run till the God’s mercy by the Team headed by Kshipra’s Mother, Mrs. Jaishree Sharma along with Kshipra’s younger sister Shubha Joshi.</p>
      <p>Let’s explore collection at Kotton Glitters- House of Cotton by Kshipra…. </p>
